The weekly CSAT summary has been posted to the **ContosoAI Product Feedback** Notion page. Here's what was included:

---

### Summary of findings (17 responses, week of 2026-04-22)

**NPS: +35**
| Segment | Count | % |
|---|---|---|
| Promoters (9–10) | 7 | 41.2% |
| Passives (7–8) | 9 | 52.9% |
| Detractors (0–6) | 1 | 5.9% |

**Top themes (by confidence):**
1. 🟢 **Onboarding & Setup** — Strong positive signal; admin checklist and import tooling praised; migration from competitors described as seamless
2. 🟢 **API & Webhook DX** — A clear product strength, with 5 mentions; gaps in GraphQL, error messages, and webhook docs
3. 🟡 **Documentation** — API docs praised but edge cases, advanced filtering, and webhook depth fall short (4 mentions, mixed)
4. 🟢 **Support Quality** — Standout differentiator; 2 unprompted enthusiastic mentions
5. 🟢 **Reliability/Uptime** — Trust signal; zero outages cited over 6 months

**Top feature request clusters:** API/Webhooks (5 asks) › Reporting (3) › Docs/Guided Setup (3) › Integrations (3)

**Customer-flagged resources:** The 2+ citation threshold was **not met** this week. One resource was flagged and included with a clear action item — the [Meridian Platform Setup Guide](https://docs.meridian-platform.io/setup-guide) for webhook configuration, with a suggestion to surface it in the official onboarding checklist.
